title: DataRescue_IDA_Pro_Advanced_v5.2.zip
description:
IDA Pro is a Windows or Linux hosted multi-processor disassembler and debugger that
offers so many features it is hard to describe them all.

Version 5.2 of our IDA Pro Disassembler & Debugger keeps its graph based interface,
its enhancements in the area of stack tracking but introduces a scriptable debugger,
improves its stack tracking capabilities, ads iPhone disassembly support,
new ARM architectures support (more than 200 new instructions), improves the PowerPC
module and a lot of usability features.
